Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.74,0:00:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自古以來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們就對妖怪心存畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而妖怪們的統帥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領軍「百鬼夜行」的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們稱之為妖怪的總帥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賦予其別稱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魑魅魍魎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.47,0:00:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「滑頭鬼」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？少主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪女 看 月亮很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都能像這樣安穩的渡過就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕好的百鬼夜行之日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸生將謀反之人牛鬼安置在身邊的決意十分堅定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 此時在西方的地域已經吹起進險惡之風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸生 現在仍未覺察到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fad(200,0)\bord3\be4\3c&H27275F&}魔鏡降臨 吞食果實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又做了那個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從六歲開始一直反覆做的那個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個糟糕的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是那個奇怪的夢弄得我沒睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 你才六歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 等你長大了我們再玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約好了哦 我會來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？那是什麼？什麼約定？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是島
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少青賽日本代表當之無愧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們幫忙 青田坊……不對……是倉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}加油 加油 少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點事情不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 加油 少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝你一直的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 是這樣 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了保護自己不受妖怪襲擊的禹步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去糟取精的改良版啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非得學這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了你們好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還想在全裸時被妖怪襲擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約定到底是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 家長同學也來上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我最希望你能學會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你貌似很有妖怪緣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 來試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 各位 在練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個也能算禹步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍天之下學習陰陽之術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多燦爛的一頁青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼來召開最新消息妖怪體驗談大會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 首先
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家長同學 今天是你的生日吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於自家人的禮物不必客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就速速地收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裏面裝的什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個盒子是名牌貨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詛……詛咒人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是家長同學的妖怪化人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 超可愛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰要那種東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是高級名牌定製品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀 多餘的解釋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 清繼同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不聽發表會了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我有點睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下就做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來只要把這些送回教室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還要準備做飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒問題的 別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主的事就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太晚回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請早點回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很高興收到生日禮物 但是這個實在……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你生日那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會去接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道紫色鏡子的故事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫色的鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 妖怪雲外鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通稱紫色的鏡子 被稱為能照出魔物的鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說看了這面鏡子的人會受到詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在十三歲的生日被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車站有這麼遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被殺？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是十三歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在妖怪的世界從以前開始就把十三歲作為成人的年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說成為大人就會被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 果實成熟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 奴良同學 你遲到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才在打掃教室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 加奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十三歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 我來接你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 我們一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續七年前的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 我不知道那些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊？從夢裏出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉迷藏? 你跑不掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 禹步 但是我都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是？學校? 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在鏡子裏玩捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該是在去車站的路上 但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…… 為什麼卻回到學校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫色的鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 你才六歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等你長大了我們再玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約好了哦 我會來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:10:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你十三歲生日那天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候的……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈這間屋子裏沒有鏡子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很擠哦 很擠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雲外鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒聽說過 也許是某地被驅逐出組的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這樣啊  今天是加奈的生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊 說起剛才的生日禮物 其實還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真過分 這可是我妖怪化的可愛人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出不去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鏡子 又出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:10:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 聽得見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清繼同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很吃驚吧 其實這個人偶裏面裝了手機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為清十字團的通訊工具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命 我現在正被鏡子的妖怪襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家長同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 你現在在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校的某個男廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家長同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪裏的男廁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清繼同學你們到那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去這邊找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清繼同學 等等 我在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼看不到我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人會來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 能看到這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏只屬於我跟加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 要被吸進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 少在我的地盤上對女人出手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 你是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少來礙我好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分不清哪個是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分不清是哪個的話 全數盡砍便是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家長同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家長同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 那個… 這個 貌似是我誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點沒睡醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡眼朦朧地看到這個人偶才會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被鼠妖抓住的時候 還有上次合宿的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都是陸生在的時候就會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 拜託你 再多陪我呆一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多說點你的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算會給你帶來恐怖的回憶也不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 害怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不害怕 跟你在一起 所以不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這裏是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道我的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會好好地告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的是……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到本店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日來到本妖怪和風飯店「化貓店」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱烈歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生意不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來經營的不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上吧 我不會再出什麼紕漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 這個女孩不是被舊鼠擄去的人類女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她帶到這裏來好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 良太貓 能拜託你件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主也不是省油的燈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然帶了個這麼可愛的情人來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家吃醋了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說少主是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人真的是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二 不 今天滿十三歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是你生日?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可喜可賀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你從今天開始就是大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是值得慶賀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成為一個出色的妖怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被發現你是人類的話 說不定等下會被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶吶 你是什麼妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…… 那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 我會被吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是你生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個娃娃好可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏買的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家也想要個哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪的世界是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟想像的有些不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～ 妖怪真的是各型各色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飽了 吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流屋的老婆婆做的東西就是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主真是的 都這個點兒了 還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼叫少主就包在我身上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把少主給看丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓咪 木天蓼汁好好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠盡興真是再好不過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 陸生那傢伙是到早上才回來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 早上才回的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙也挺行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那孩子挺行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這是幹了什麼好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會做出昨天那種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 少主 你昨晚到今早到底在哪裏幹什麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 昨晚抱歉…… 啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸生 我有事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想問我什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把至今為止的行為之類的聯繫起來讓我想到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要陸生在 那個人也會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說陸生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 露餡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你 告訴我有關那個人的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不太明白是怎麼回事 你為什麼想知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問下而已嘛 跟陸生你沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 還沒有開門營業的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 好大的聲響啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三郎貓 你的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剛才那陣驟風弄的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 只不過是衣服破了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去換件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破了而已?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是一無所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴良組一組看來是跟傳聞所言一樣的嫩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偵查真是來對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴良組的根據地 浮世繪町
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是偵查這個城市很快就能找到他們老窩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花了一個禮拜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個冰冷的傢伙真是感覺拘束的不自在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼呢 阿青
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說什麼冷勒 扣子全開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個季節還系圍巾?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.29,0:23:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 滑頭鬼之孫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.11,0:23:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從西面吹來的先驅之風
